<h1>Welcome</h1>
    <p>
    Welcome to the Survalyser documentation! Survalyser is a survival analysis
    program which is capable of producing Kaplan-Meier curves & Cox Regression. 
    </p>

    <p>
    This documentation contains three sections:
    <ul>
    <li><b>Loading Data:</b>
      This section discuss how to prepare your data before loading it into
      survalyser.
    </li>
    <li><b>The Spreadsheet:</b>
      This section discusses how to use the spreadsheet to filter & process
      the data you've loaded in before analysis.
    </li>
    <li><b>Analysis:</b>
      This section discusses how to use the various analysis tools to generate
      charts & calculate various statistical quantities.
    </li>
    
<div>